des:
Welcome to the WNED, WBFO Alexa Skill.

Once you've enabled the skill, say "Alexa, open WNED WBFO" then say:
"Listen live" or "Play WBFO", if you would like to hear WBFO-FM
"Play Classical WNED”, if you would like to hear Classical WNED-FM
"Play Jazzworks”, if you would like to hear Jazzworks on WBFO-HD2

Thank you for listening to “your” public radio stations in Western New York and Southern Ontario on your connected Alexa Devices.
